'''Hull skimming''' was a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] tactic in which fighters would strafe a [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ship]] at distances of around five meters above the [[Hull/Legends|hull]]. The goal was to allow for point-blank accuracy in targeting vital systems, as well as evading ships' defensive weaponry.

